Package: riasecco
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian RIASEC Vocational Guidance with Colombian SNIES Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andres", "Romero", email = "me@afromero.co",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Bayesian adaptive RIASEC quiz engine paired with
    Colombia's SNIES (Sistema Nacional de Información de la Educación
    Superior) program database. Provides the complete catalog of 17,230
    active higher education programs, IPIP RIASEC item banks in English
    and Spanish, and a recommendation engine with enrollment-weighted
    priors. Designed for vocational guidance in underserved regions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/afromero/riasec-co
BugReports: https://github.com/afromero/riasec-co/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
